19-06-13T23:06:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:33:04.000Z","msg":"的確兩者冇衝突冇矛盾<br />\n等於七一遊行各有表態<br />\n其實咁樣反而對於世界而言七一遊行就好似新年嘉年華咁樣，不能反應事件嚴重性。<br />\n我唔反對各自表態。<br />\n我唔希望見到表態失焦！<br />\n燃眉之急係逃犯條例<br />\n槍口一致拉倒惡法，繼續遊行黑警譴責追究及立法防止同類黑警事件發生。咁樣ge警力亂用嚴重表達監警會ge能力不足，警權過大！<br />\n都係後續活動同埋訴求表達<br />\n唔好俾林鄭用黑警黎撕裂市民撕裂家庭！<br />\n當家庭被撕裂，年輕人心理上長期落黎會矛盾會疲勞會退縮！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反送中！香港人加油！</span>"},{"pid":"aee5f208143294b50e1b35980cad0819c27bad70","tid":1217811,"uid":33799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:59:26.000Z","msg":"認同，16.6 唔應該太聚焦黑警"},{"pid":"db897a0516725e4f7ef04108a6fcdd733bf61bf5","tid":1217811,"uid":220182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:59:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a610a0670d271532ce492db3bd1b16ad978551d2","tid":1217811,"uid":61611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:01:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"758926c2e1ed9be4e92ac7b5ccdf22c36765c46e","tid":1217811,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:10:57.000Z","msg":"推 反送中先係主角"},{"pid":"7614ff502557c80730b302eb261b598e9cd59b4f","tid":1217811,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:11:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fb14bcbcf71b611514f5c4c3bc4441f637cf6c18","tid":1217811,"uid":260169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:20:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"49cb85bbc27b3123685591c697ffaf8f97c96d7d","tid":1217811,"uid":260169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"77e8ca9cc68657b63c70a66a1579fda75281ef92","tid":1217811,"uid":28974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6349de4bfda7a62642fa793dab8b628da88b776","tid":1217811,"uid":260169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit